Section 4.4.2 Other Requirements
C. Off-Street Parking. Off-street parking shall be provided in accordance with the requirements
in Chapter 6.
llm_outputs.rationale: The document specifies that off-street parking requirements for the R-O Residential Office District are detailed in Chapter 6.
